models.name: Gemma 2B IT (int8)
models.description: A lightweight, state-of-the-art open model built from the same research and technology used to create the Gemini models. Optimized for CPU with 8-bit quantization.

models.name: Phi-3.5 Instruct (q8)
models.description: Unofficial Phi-3.5-mini-instruct model converted to TFLite for on-device text generation and summarization.

models.name: LLaMA-3.2 1B (q8)
models.description: The LLaMA 3.2 1B model is a compact, high-performing language model designed for a variety of NLP tasks, quantized to 8-bit for on-device efficiency.

models.name: MobileBERT Classifier
models.description: A lightweight and fast BERT variant optimized for text classification on resource-constrained mobile and edge devices.

models.name: BlenderBot Small (90M)
models.description: TFLite version of BlenderBot Small (90M) for conversational tasks. A dialogue model that can chat and engage in open-domain conversations.
